node.text: Join DeVonn Francis and Joel Moore as they show you how to throw a fun Pride party this year through cooking, music, and decor, while chatting about fun places to go to in the NYC area. This event, along with the sales of the #LimitedEdition Pride watch will benefit the @trevorproject #PrideOnFossil

node.title: Pride on with @tuna__turner and @moorehisstyle. Benefiting the @trevorproje

node.text: Join Lezley Crawford as she takes us through what she’s most excited about for our falls bags!

node.title: Behind the design with Lezley Crawford

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 08, 2021. May be an image of purse and saddle-stitched leather.

node.text: Back-to-school season, whatever type of school it is.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 06, 2021. May be an image of saddle-stitched leather, purse and text that says 'n FOSSIL'.

node.text: Our go-to tote (for every season). Kier is a vegan leather tote cut from a totally different cloth. Actually, it’s cactus. 🌵🏜

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 05, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch and saddle-stitched leather.

node.text: "We refined Bronson using bold, stick indices that bring the focus back to its stopwatch function.”–David Matthews, Men’s Watch Designer

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 04, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text: His watch for fall: Bronson, now in a sized-down 44mm case.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 03, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text: You want Stella? You got Stella. The most-loved bestseller is back—for good.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 02, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text: Say hello to our new collection of Vintage Classics. Rooted in the past, made for today.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on July 31, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch and text.

node.text: When in doubt, wear the Neutra chronograph watch.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on July 30, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch and saddle-stitched leather.

node.text: In the mood for... vintage films. Tell us what your weekend plans look like in the comments below.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on July 29, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text: Watch of the day: the Bronson chronograph in a 50mm case.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on July 28, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch and indoor.

node.text: The art of watchmaking. Let us know what you want to see more of on our channel in the comments below!
